---
title: Honey-Roasted Squash with Warm Mushroom & Quinoa Salad
description: Roasting with a touch of honey helps caramelize this creamy acorn squash. The sweetness from the squash and golden raisins pair perfectly with salty feta and nutty quinoa in this hearty grain salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54e495496ced6e0b1c8b4568.jpg
